				<td colspan="2"><span>A set of Gothic Steel LDoN smithed armor should do you nicely until you are around lvl 40.
<br />

<br />
Bards are arguably the LEAST gear-dependent class in the game.  You should get nice instruments and weapons though.
<br />

<br />
Thuderous Drum of Karana
<br />
Lute of the Howler
<br />
Troubador's Mace (1hb and Brass Instrument)
<br />
Bloodstained Flute
<br />
Battle Drummer's Main Gauche (Piercer, also percussion)
<br />
Insert_1hs_here...
<br />

